* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/ef8f5ca8-d013-4422-a47a-41c5e4ce5dc8/16451.jpg?format=original)

The Miz goes to speak to Nick Aldis about Championship opportunities. Aldis says he already spoke to Carmelo Hayes and says "It's all his".

Miz seems to think he's talking about the Tag titles, but Aldis doesn't tell him it's about the US title.

Carmelo walks up to Sami Zayn to call his shot but the Miz was listening. He asks why Melo isn't following Miz guidance to Tag Team gold.

Melo asks why can't he win both? Miz has done it. But the Miz doesn't seem to appreciate this.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1e2cd7f2-8661-4b6f-960f-f3946900e143/16450.jpg?format=original)

Rey Mysterio agrees to put the AAA Mega Championship around Dom's waist if he wins tonight.

Finn Balor comes up to Dom and tells him if he wants to be the greatest Luchadore then he needs to win the Championship on his own.

Then Balor takes his wife and leaves.

